            "body": "  Thank you very much for the swift responce!\r\n\r\n  Could you provide an example use? My mostly poor command-line skills are only producing a string of \"Aborted (core dumped)\" \r\n\r\n  Also, a question: Will busy_start, busy_stop work for only one mode (the insert mode,) or will it apply universally?\r\n\r\n Mu OS is linux and my terminal kitty. (Although I am not married to the terminal if it is the one causing issues.)\r\n\r\nAgain, thank you.",
